@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bdbewf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((0.21 * tmp))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.52) / (tmp + 0.84 + v0 + 0.08)) + ((v1 + 0.88 / v0 + 0.24) + wp.abs(tmp + 0.62)))
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.sin(v1 + 0.08) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.74)))
    v0 = 0.02
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.80)))
    data[tid] = v0
